Validation in Arkivya

Learn how to add client side validation.

Step 1: Click on "Builder" link

It will open Arkivya Builder.

Step 2: Click on "Create New Form" button

Step 3: Click on "e.g., Customer Feedback"

Step 4: Type "Validation" in "Form Name" field

Step 5: Click Chat icon.

Step 6: Click on "Create Form" button

Step 7: Click on "Add Field" button

Step 8: Click on "Text" button

Step 9: Click on "Text"

Step 10: Type "Enter your name" in "Write here..." field

Step 11: Click on "Write here..."

Step 12: Type "maximum " in "Write here..." field

Step 13: Type "maximum 10 letters." in "Write here..." field
